f=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104uwa1665702797496.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uwa1665702797496.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uwa1665702797496.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uwa1665702797496\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n Panel Library \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use this editor to define panels that can be used as toolbars for an application or form component.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__p_d6896e1_d6897e1_d6898e1\">Panels contain buttons to execute structure editor functions and activate component operations. Operation buttons appear only in form panels and session panels; they are ignored in pop-up panels.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__section_i3t_myf_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d960636e58\">Properties</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__ul_fvx_myf_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__li_d3377e1_d3378e1_d3379e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__li_d3380e1_d3381e1_d3382e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ymp1665702709794.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ymp1665702709794.html\" title=\"Function to include in the panel. A function can be a user-defined operation or a structure editor function, or it can represent a new line or a separator.\">Function</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__li_d3383e1_d3384e1_d3385e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vkx1665702687952.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vkx1665702687952.html\" title=\"This property determines whether buttons for character attributes (bold, italics, and underline) are displayed when the panel is used as a session panel. Valid values are True or False.\">Character Attributes</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__li_d3386e1_d3387e1_d3388e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xmm1665702688023.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xmm1665702688023.html\" title=\"Determines whether buttons for View, Overstrike, and Previous mode should appear in the panel when it is used as a session panel.\">View</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__li_d3389e1_d3390e1_d3391e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zga1665702688096.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zga1665702688096.html\" title=\"Number of available Uniface character sets (Font 0 through Font 7) for which a button is displayed when this panel is used as a session panel. Valid values are 0 through 7.\">Font Range</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__li_d3392e1_d3393e1_d3394e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vfq1665702709863.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vfq1665702709863.html\" title=\"Height of the panel button, in character cells.\">Height</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__li_d3395e1_d3396e1_d3397e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sag1665702709934.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sag1665702709934.html\" title=\"Width of the button, in characters.\">Width</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__li_d3398e1_d3399e1_d3400e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nct1665702710006.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nct1665702710006.html\" title=\"Name of the operation activated by this button. If the operation does not exist in the form with which that this panel is associated, this button is disabled.\">Operation</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__li_d3401e1_d3402e1_d3403e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uzw1665702710075.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uzw1665702710075.html\" title=\"Name of the glyph to be used as the icon of an operation button in a form panel. If there is a message with the same name as the glyph, it is used as the tooltip for the button.\">Glyph Name &amp; Message Text</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__section_gfd_4yf_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d960636e161\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__p_d6905e1_d6906e1_d6907e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jyy1705583151243.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jyy1705583151243.html\" title=\"Panels are global objects that are used to define toolbars or floating palettes in desktop applications. They can be associated with a form component or an application shell.\">Working with Panels</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__section_mwp_pyf_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d960636e176\">Menu Options</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Frequently-Used Menu Options for Panels</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__1\">Menu Option </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__2\">Action </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt; Open/New</span></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__2\">Create a new global object </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt; Open</span></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__2\">Open a new library. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt; Duplicate</span></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__2\">Save a copy of the current panel under a different\n                name. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt; Delete</span></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__2\">Delete the current global object. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt; Compile</span></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__2\">Compile the current panel. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">View &gt;Zoom Field</span></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__2\">Edit the selected field in a separate dialog; useful\n                when editing text blocks and code. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">View &gt;Message Frame</span></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__2\">Display the message frame; useful after compiling the\n                object. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Go To</span>\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">&lt;Global Object Type&gt;</var>\n</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uwa1665702797496__table_d590e1_d591e1_d592e1__entry__2\">Create or open a different type of global object, or\n                library (properties). </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zja1665702873395.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Panels</a><p>Panels are global objects that are typically used to create toolbars for form components and application shells. They contain buttons to execute structure editor functions and activate component operations.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532870\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532870\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Panel Library Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Panel Library Use this editor to define panels that can be used as toolbars for an application or form component. Panels contain buttons to execute structure editor functions and activate component operations. Operation buttons appear only in form panels and session panels; they are ignored in pop-up panels. Properties Description Function Character Attributes View Font Range Height Width Operation Glyph Name & Message Text How to Working with Panels Menu Options Table 1. Frequently-Used Menu Options for Panels Menu Option Action File > Open/New Create a new global object File > Open Open a new library. File > Duplicate Save a copy of the current panel under a different name. File > Delete Delete the current global object. File > Compile Compile the current panel. View >Zoom Field Edit the selected field in a separate dialog; useful when editing text blocks and code. View >Message Frame Display the message frame; useful after compiling the object. Go To <Global Object Type> Create or open a different type of global object, or library (properties). Related Links Panels Panels are global objects that are typically used to create toolbars for form components and application shells. They contain buttons to execute structure editor functions and activate component operations. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}